OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales is de-
OL,7,Fescalating Ysbyty Glan Clwyd in Rhyl
OL,8,Ffrom it's 'needs significant
OL,9,Fimprovement' status, following an
OL,10,Funannounced follow-up inspection of
OL,11,Fthe Emergency Department.
OL,13,FIn May 2022, the department, run by
OL,14,FBetsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,15,FBoard, was designated as a Service
OL,16,FRequiring Significant Improvement
OL,17,F(SRSI).
OL,19,FA follow-up inspection in November
OL,20,F2022 found only minimal improvement
OL,21,Fand the designation remained in place.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
