OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,FBut during the recent inspection over
OL,7,Fthree consecutive days in April/May
OL,8,F2024 HIW say they "found a marked
OL,9,Fimprovement within the areas of
OL,10,Fsignificant concern identified in
OL,11,F2022."
OL,13,FThese areas included the timely
OL,14,Fescalation of patients with critical
OL,15,Fand high-risk conditions, and
OL,16,Fstrengthened oversight of the waiting
OL,17,Farea compared to previous inspections.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
