OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,FOverall, inspectors highlighted an
OL,7,Fimproved culture, an increasing in
OL,8,Fstaffing levels and stronger
OL,9,Fleadership.
OL,11,FThey say that because of these
OL,12,Fimprovements, they are able to de-
OL,13,Fescalate the service.
OL,15,FDespite the de-escalation they say
OL,16,F"several issues remain for the service
OL,17,Fwhich continues to operate in highly
OL,18,Fdemanding and challenging conditions.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
