OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,F"Areas of concern included excessive
OL,7,Fwaiting times, inadequate processes
OL,8,Ffor issues with medication management,
OL,9,Fand insufficient checks of life-saving
OL,10,Fequipment.
OL,12,F"We noted that oversight of the unit's
OL,13,Fwaiting room had improved with patient
OL,14,Femergencies escalated and well managed.
OL,16,F"Overall, the department was clean and
OL,17,Ftidy, with robust infection prevention
OL,18,Fand control measures in place; and
OL,19,Fgeneral health and safety risks
OL,20,Fassessed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
