OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,F"However, we were concerned that
OL,7,Fpressure and demand within the
OL,8,Fdepartment was leading to an increased
OL,9,Frisk to patients. "
OL,11,FThey identified a poor flow of
OL,12,Fpatients from the point of admission
OL,13,Fto discharge as a continuing issue.
OL,15,F"During the inspection there were
OL,16,Faround 50 patients each day who were
OL,17,Fdeemed well-enough to be discharged
OL,18,Fwith the unit at full bed capacity.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
