OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,F"However, their discharge was delayed
OL,7,Ffor various reasons such as waiting
OL,8,Ffor further rehabilitation, a care
OL,9,Fpackage to be put in place or a
OL,10,Fplacement in another care facility.
OL,12,F"Patients were waiting roughly four
OL,13,Fhours for treatment within the
OL,14,Fdepartment, with just under a quarter
OL,15,Fof patients waiting over twelve hours
OL,16,Fbefore being seen."
OL,18,FInspectors found that one patient was
OL,19,Fnot seen by a doctor for over 10 hours
OL,20,Fwith a suspected neck of femur
OL,21,Ffracture, and no record of pain relief.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
