OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,FThey say some patients also told them
OL,7,Fthey had waited up to 48 hours and had
OL,8,Fnot been informed or updated on their
OL,9,Fcare and treatment plans.
OL,11,FInspectors saw evidence of strong
OL,12,Fstaff communication during shift
OL,13,Fhandovers, and good working
OL,14,Frelationships within the department
OL,15,Fand with ambulance staff. Inspectors
OL,16,Fwitnessed positive staff to patient
OL,17,Finteractions, with staff treating
OL,18,Fpatients with dignity and respect,
OL,19,Fdespite challenging conditions.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
