OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,FThey said "it was concerning to note
OL,7,Fthat some patients, who needed either
OL,8,Fpressure area risk assessments, or
OL,9,Ffalls risks assessments, didn't
OL,10,Freceive these assessments until they
OL,11,Fhad been in the department for over
OL,12,Fsix hours.
OL,14,F"Consequently, adjustments were not
OL,15,Fimmediately in place for those at risk
OL,16,Fdue to mobility issues, or increased
OL,17,Ffragility.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
