OL,3,CYsbyty Glan Clwyd de-escalated from
OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,F"There were often delays in patients
OL,7,Freceiving treatment from specialist
OL,8,Fdoctors, an area identified for
OL,9,Fimprovement in the unit's previous
OL,10,Finspection.
OL,12,F"It was also concerning to find
OL,13,Fresuscitation equipment, such as a
OL,14,Fdefibrillator in one room had not seen
OL,15,Fchecked since early January 2024."
OL,17,FInspectors found that only three in
OL,18,Ften patients were triaged within the
OL,19,Fnational recommended time limit of 15
OL,20,Fminutes, with the average being
OL,21,Fapproximately 58 minutes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
