OL,6,FImprovements were also required to
OL,7,Fensure that Do Not Attempt
OL,8,FCardiopulmonary Resuscitation (DNACPR)
OL,9,Fdiscussions are accurately recorded
OL,10,Fand readily available to staff.
OL,12,FA plan has been produced by the Health
OL,13,FBoard, which contains a comprehensive
OL,14,Fset of actions to address the wide
OL,15,Frange of further improvements needed.
OL,17,FAlun Jones, Chief Executive of
OL,18,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales, said
OL,19,F"The pressure and demand on healthcare
OL,20,Fservices continues to create
OL,21,Fsignificant challenges for the NHS.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
