OL,4,C'needs significant improvement' status
OL,6,F"During this inspection we found staff
OL,7,Fworking extremely hard in challenging
OL,8,Fconditions to provide patients with
OL,9,Fsafe and effective care.
OL,11,F"It is reassuring to see improvements
OL,12,Fhave been made since our previous
OL,13,Finspections of the department, but
OL,14,Ffurther improvement is still needed.
OL,16,F"I hope this report will provide the
OL,17,Fhealth board with a clear
OL,18,Funderstanding of the challenges being
OL,19,Ffaced by the service and support the
OL,20,Faction they need to improve.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
